title: [HiFi|Scan] Marvel Team-Up: Spider-Man + Human Torch (1972|Jojo)
description:
Q: "HiFi"? Whatnow?? Wherefore???

A: This is the very first of many Hitlist Fills torrents (HiFi for short), in which
   I shall do my level best to upload everything released since 2012-04-11 but, for
   whatever reason, not included in the regular Weeklies, nor torrented separately
   in the meantime in some other form. In other words, the prefix means that you
   probably haven't seen these releases before - not hereabouts, at any rate!
   
   Unlike for the Digital Hitlists, to which these uploads constitute a sequel of 
   sorts, bundling is going to be primarily by title instead of by release date.
   There are various reasons for that choice, not the least of which being that the
   latter is in some cases known only very vaguely. The bit after "HiFi" specifies
   what kind of scans the torrent contains; these will be explained along the way.
   
   So, with a quick thanks to Vik for the initial impetus and without further ado...
